    Tarantulas looked up from the bloddy Rat Trap. "I have no clue....you 
might want to scan for her. I bet shes with some other bot....." And then 
shut his commlink. He wanted to make Quickstrike paranoid.

    Megatron nodded. Excellent. This was a good idea. "Good....and when shall 
we decide on the Maximal matter?"

    Nighteyes glared with a smile. Megatron was going to love this. "Well, 
Ill be going now. Um....but I wouldnt make any long term plans. Tee Hee 
Hee..." She laughed and walked away. Her optronic eye camera was sending the 
images right back to Megatron lair. When he got home he was going to be mad.
    Being a spy was good.
